<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
	<title>Task Creator</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/table.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/checkbox.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
	
	<!-- Нормализация стилей -->
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/normalize/8.0.0/normalize.css">
	<script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7.1/jquery.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
	<script src="funcApp.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="section-block-header"><h1>TASK MANAGER</h1></div>
	<div class="start-page" id="main">
		<section id="home">
			<div class="section-block" id="selection-block1">
				<div class="row-block">
					<div class="column-block">
						<div class="greeting-line"><h2>Hey, do you want<br> to manage your time?</h2></div>
						<div class="header-block-text">
								<h3>Time Management Begins with Organization.</h3>
								<p>Time management isn’t this elusive form of Black Magic that so few understand. 
								In fact, anyone can efficiently manage their time as long as they get organized first. 
								Without organization, it’s difficult to see just what needs to be accomplished in the day and how important each of those things are to your long-term goals.
								</p>
							</div>
					</div>
					<div class="column-block">
						<ul class="border">
							<li><h3>Step #1 – Set Clear Goals</h3></li>
							<li><h3>Step #2 – Get Organized</h3></li>
							<li><h3>Step #3 – Prioritizing Time</h3></li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>	
			</div>
		</section>
		<section id="tasks">
				
			<div class="table-section-block" id="table-section-block1">
					<% include ../partials/table %>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		<section id="TaskInfo1" class="TaskInfo">
				<% include ../partials/taskInfo %>
			
		</section>
	</div>
	<aside>
		<div id="sidebar">
		<div class="toggle-btn" onclick="toggleSidebar(this)">
			<span class="bar1"></span>
			<span class="bar2"></span>
			<span class="bar3"></span>
		</div>
		<ul class="sidebar">
			<li onclick="dropdownHome('toggle-btn')">Home</li>
			<li onclick="dropdown('toggle-btn')">Tasks</li>
			<li onclick="dropdownTaskInfo()">Create Task</li>
			<li>Contact</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	</aside>
	
</body>
</html>